Yeah, it's very neat.

9
00:00:51,322 --> 00:00:54,784
My parents always sided
with my elder sister.

10
00:00:57,162 --> 00:00:58,329
I'm home.

11
00:01:04,961 --> 00:01:06,921
They're not the biggest agency,

12
00:01:07,005 --> 00:01:10,133
but many of their talents
are in dramas and magazines.

13
00:01:10,216 --> 00:01:14,012
They said I could be on TV
if I worked hard and took lessons.

14
00:01:14,095 --> 00:01:15,722
Are you being serious?

15
00:01:15,805 --> 00:01:19,475
I am. I'm going to quit school
and move to Tokyo soon.

16
00:01:19,559 --> 00:01:21,477
Don't be foolish.

17
00:01:21,561 --> 00:01:23,730
It's not going to be that easy.

18
00:01:24,480 --> 00:01:26,107
What do you mean, "foolish?"

19
00:01:27,233 --> 00:01:29,736
At least go to college first.

20
00:01:34,866 --> 00:01:35,909
Riko.

21
00:01:36,659 --> 00:01:38,411
I'm not the same as you.

22
00:01:38,494 --> 00:01:42,081
I'll live my life my own way!

23
00:01:42,916 --> 00:01:44,751
Hey, wait. Riko!

24
00:01:54,260 --> 00:01:57,847
I wanted to make my family accept me.

25
00:02:02,727 --> 00:02:06,481
After defying my parents' wishes,
I found myself breathing the Tokyo air,

26
00:02:07,357 --> 00:02:09,859
which was murky and full of exhaust fumes.

27
00:02:10,777 --> 00:02:14,155
But to me, it was the smell of freedom.

28
00:02:14,906 --> 00:02:16,783
A smell I didn't have back home.

29
00:02:18,618 --> 00:02:20,245
Here we are.

30
00:02:20,745 --> 00:02:22,664
Feel free to use the slippers.

31
00:02:23,665 --> 00:02:26,709
This one was built 50 years ago.

32
00:02:27,210 --> 00:02:31,381
And it's far from the station
with no automatic lock on the door,

33
00:02:31,464 --> 00:02:34,467
so it's not the best place
for a woman to live alone.

34
00:02:34,550 --> 00:02:38,429
But considering your budget,
this is about what you can get.

35
00:02:41,432 --> 00:02:44,560
Everything related to water usage
should be relatively new, though.

36
00:02:47,188 --> 00:02:53,111
But if I recall, the water heater
for the bath is an older model.

37
00:02:58,741 --> 00:02:59,993
I'll take it.

38
00:03:00,785 --> 00:03:02,245
MK PROMOTION

39
00:03:02,328 --> 00:03:03,871
This will be your stage name.

40
00:03:04,706 --> 00:03:05,790
Risa Hirayama.

41
00:03:05,873 --> 00:03:08,501
You'll have to pass
the trial period first, though.

42
00:03:08,584 --> 00:03:10,795
Your lessons will cost 30,000 yen monthly.

43
00:03:11,546 --> 00:03:16,551
Whether you get officially signed on
with us will depend on your performance.

44
00:03:17,719 --> 00:03:21,180
Sorry, I was told my lesson fees
would be covered for me.

45
00:03:21,848 --> 00:03:24,517
Oh, that's only
after you are officially signed on.

46
00:03:28,021 --> 00:03:28,813
Is that okay?

47
00:03:30,023 --> 00:03:31,607
Yes, I understand.

48
00:03:31,691 --> 00:03:32,775
Good.

49
00:03:37,780 --> 00:03:40,992
I started part-time work
to cover my lesson fees.

50
00:03:41,701 --> 00:03:44,037
Ms. Hirata, restock the drinks after that.

51
00:03:44,120 --> 00:03:45,038
Okay.

52
