-Ms. Hirayama, put more emotion in it.
-Okay.

60
00:04:04,098 --> 00:04:08,603
Unfortunately, we will not be
signing you on this time either.

61
00:04:09,812 --> 00:04:10,938
I see.

62
00:04:11,606 --> 00:04:13,149
But you're really close.

63
00:04:13,232 --> 00:04:16,152
How about you keep
taking lessons a little longer?

64
00:04:18,404 --> 00:04:20,239
Look, it's not just me.

65
00:04:20,323 --> 00:04:23,534
Others in the agency agree
there's something special about you!

66
00:04:26,204 --> 00:04:27,622
Let's keep trying.

67
00:04:30,708 --> 00:04:32,168
Okay, I will.

68
