-Hope it's not an issue.

70
00:04:38,883 --> 00:04:40,259
Please sign here.

71
00:04:42,136 --> 00:04:43,137
Right here.

72
00:04:45,723 --> 00:04:46,599
Okay.

73
00:04:51,771 --> 00:04:53,272
