77
00:05:03,741 --> 00:05:06,828
And yet,
all I could do was trust his words.

78
00:05:06,911 --> 00:05:08,121
Sorry for the wait.

79
00:05:10,456 --> 00:05:11,874
-Stay away!
-Stop.

80
00:05:11,958 --> 00:05:13,251
Don't do it!

81
00:05:13,334 --> 00:05:14,836
This doesn't concern you two.

82
00:05:14,919 --> 00:05:17,672
Do you have any idea how I feel?
How could you?

83
00:05:18,381 --> 00:05:20,925
-Let's switch now.
-Okay.

84
00:05:27,723 --> 00:05:30,852
Stay away. This doesn't concern you two.

85
00:05:30,935 --> 00:05:31,769
RIKO HIRATA

86
00:05:38,818 --> 00:05:41,821
Before I knew it, three years had gone by.

