a sense of normalcy on the outside.

253
00:20:28,957 --> 00:20:32,461
I would remember
that day less and less often.

254
00:20:33,462 --> 00:20:35,088
To a secure future.

255
00:20:36,340 --> 00:20:37,341
However…

256
00:20:39,426 --> 00:20:43,805
I hadn't gotten over it even a little bit.

257
00:20:48,310 --> 00:20:52,397
We want to protect your smile
and the smiles of those dear to you.

258
00:20:54,107 --> 00:20:56,526
Japan Sanwa Insurance.

259
00:20:56,610 --> 00:21:03,658
Why did I, the victim, have to suffer,
while he, the assailant, gets to smile?

260
00:21:05,911 --> 00:21:10,290
At that moment,
I felt immense rage for the first time.

261
00:21:12,125 --> 00:21:13,919
I can't forgive him.

262
00:21:14,002 --> 00:21:15,337
I refuse to.

